## Limitations

The findings in this report are based on available online resources and may not encompass all perspectives on the topic. The search was limited to English-language sources, which may exclude relevant information from non-English publications. Additionally, the dynamic nature of lobbying means that its role and impact can vary significantly across different political contexts and over time.